in%20part%20because%20the%20move%20was%20overwhelming.%20There%20were%20boxes%20to%20unpack%2C%20and%20she%20didn't%20have%20any%20friends%20or%20family%20in%20the%20area.%20Instead%2C%20she%20focused%20on%20settling%20in%20and%20building%20her%20social%20and%20professional%20network%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20came%20to%20San%20Francisco%2C%20I%20really%20had%20no%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mandal%20began%20her%20job%20search%20in%20September%202024%2C%20she%20sensed%20the%20tech%20hiring%20landscape%20wasn't%20in%20her%20favor.%20To%20gain%20traction%2C%20she%20believed%20she%20needed%20to%20connect%20directly%20with%20hiring%20managers%20and%20recruiters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20simply%20applying%20to%20job%20listings%2C%20she%20looked%20for%20people%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20were%20actively%20posting%20about%20open%20product%20manager%20roles%20on%20LinkedIn.%20One%20trick%20she%20used%20was%20searching%20%26quot%3Bproduct%20manager%20%2B%20hiring%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20combination%20that%20filtered%20for%20posts%20containing%20both%20terms.%20Then%20she'd%20apply%20LinkedIn's%20%26quot%3Bpast%2024%20hours%26quot%3B%20filter%20to%20surface%20the%20newest%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20take%20things%20a%20step%20further%2C%20she'd%20tweak%20the%20URL%20manually%20%E2%80%94%20changing%20the%20number%20of%20seconds%20from%2086%2C400%20(24%20hours)%20to%203%2C600%20(1%20hour)%20%E2%80%94%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapplying-early-for-jobs-helped-gen-zer-land-internship-meta-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esee%20posts%20from%20the%20past%20hour%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20she%20found%20a%20post%20of%20interest%2C%20Mandal%20said%20she'd%20message%20the%20recruiter%20or%20hiring%20manager%20%E2%80%94%20explaining%20why%20she%20was%20interested%20in%20the%20role%20and%20why%20she%20thought%20she'd%20be%20a%20good%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20filtering%20LinkedIn%20posts%2C%20Mandal%20applied%20the%20same%20logic%20to%20the%20platform's%20job%20listings%20tab%20%E2%80%94%20using%20filters%20to%20uncover%20the%20newest%20openings.%20Based%20on%20conversations%20with%20recruiters%20and%20her%20network%2C%20she%20said%20she%20thinks%20it's%20crucial%20to%20be%20among%20the%20first%2020%20or%2030%20applicants%20for%20a%20role.%20Many%20recruiters%2C%20she%20said%2C%20are%20far%20more%20likely%20to%20closely%20review%20the%2020th%20application%20than%20the%20200th%20or%20the%202%2C000th.%20Career%20experts%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapplying-early-for-jobs-helped-gen-zer-land-internship-meta-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20among%20the%20first%20applicants%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20give%20candidates%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karishma%20Mandal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cd8fb2183847aa39d720e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKarishma%20Mandal%3Cp%3EKarishma%20Mandal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMandal%20was%20also%20strategic%20about%20how%20she%20submitted%20applications.%20She%20said%20an%20HR%20professional%20at%20one%20company%20told%20her%20they%20prioritized%20applications%20submitted%20directly%20through%20their%20website%20over%20those%20sourced%20via%20LinkedIn%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20the%20candidate%20was%20redirected%20there%20from%20a%20LinkedIn%20post.%20Mandal%20figured%20following%20that%20advice%20couldn't%20hurt%20her%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20an%20extra%20edge%2C%20Mandal%20said%20she%20used%20the%20referral%20platform%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FRefer.me%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERefer.me%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-find-job-