ring%20the%20performance%20of%20AI%20features%20on%20Instagram.%20The%20Amazon%20interview%2C%20she%20said%2C%20focused%20more%20on%20the%20company's%20leadership%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20interviews%20didn't%20ultimately%20lead%20to%20offers.%20But%20in%20late%202024%2C%20Mandal%20messaged%20a%20Salesforce%20recruiter%20on%20LinkedIn%20who%20had%20posted%20about%20an%20AI-related%20product%20manager%20role%20%E2%80%94%20and%20eventually%20heard%20back%20to%20schedule%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20several%20weeks%2C%20Mandal%20said%20she%20went%20through%20a%20seven-round%20interview%20process%20that%20included%20a%20design%20exercise%20where%20she%20was%20asked%20to%20create%20an%20AI-powered%20lawn%20mower%3B%20conversations%20with%20the%20engineering%2C%20product%2C%20and%20AI%20teams%3B%20and%20a%20final%20interview%20with%20a%20senior%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20limited%20to%20behavioral%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20Salesforce%20interviews.%20%26quot%3BMost%20hiring%20managers%20want%20to%20see%20real%20expertise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMandal%20said%20she%20received%20an%20offer%20from%20Salesforce%20around%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20which%20included%20a%20six-figure%20salary%20about%2040%25%20higher%20than%20what%20she%20earned%20in%20her%20previous%20role.%20She%20started%20full-time%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20San%20Francisco's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-san-francisco-boston-cost-living-switzerland-deutsche-bank-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20cost%20of%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20frustrating%20at%20times%2C%20she%20said%20the%20career%20benefits%20have%20made%20relocating%20from%20Chicago%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20big%20career%20move%20in%20tech%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20living%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20seeing%20how%20you%20can%20lev