0a%20rough%20few%20weeks%20for%20Zillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-my-zestimate-accurate-home-prices-obsession-zillow-algorithm-homeowner-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20popular%20home-search%20portal%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20fighting%20battles%20on%20several%20fronts.%20It's%20fending%20off%20a%20flurry%20of%20high-stakes%20lawsuits%2C%20including%20an%20antitrust%20claim%20from%20the%20federal%20government.%20Its%20attempts%20to%20stem%20the%20rising%20tide%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-new-real-estate-agent-listings-rules-homebuyers-search-homes-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexclusive%20inventory%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20homes%20marketed%20for%20sale%20but%20intentionally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-rules-commissions-zillow-home-search-pocket-listings-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekept%20off%20portals%20like%20Zillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20appear%20to%20have%20fallen%20flat.%20And%20the%20company's%20chief%20rival%20in%20that%20fight%2C%20the%20real%20estate%20brokerage%20firm%20Compass%2C%20just%20announced%20a%20mammoth%20acquisition%20that%20could%20give%20it%20greater%20influence%20over%20the%20way%20America's%20homes%20are%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZillow%20promises%20its%20users%20a%20near-complete%20view%20of%20the%20housing%20market%20simply%20by%20scrolling%20on%20their%20phones.%20That%20vision%20is%20under%20threat.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-reffkin-compass-ceo-real-estate-career-rise-job-history-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECompass%20CEO%20Robert%20Reffkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20leading%20the%20charge%20toward%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-listings-real-estate-agents-hidden-clear-cooperation-decision-nar-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20fragmented%20future%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20more%20home%20listings%20are%20initially%20stashed%20away%20in%20private%20databases%2C%20available%20only%20to%20buyers%20who%20work%20with%20certain%20agents.%20Reffkin%20says%20this%20model%20would%20give%20sellers%20more%20control%20over%20where%20and%20how%20their%20homes%20are%20marketed.%20Zillow%2C%20along%20with%20many%20others%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20argues%20that%20sharing%20listings%20widely%20gives%20buyers%20a%20fair%20shake%20and%20sellers%20the%20best%20opportunity%20to%20get%20top%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20tough%20to%20bet%20against%20Zillow.%20With%20more%20than%20220%20million%20unique%20visitors%20each%20month%2C%20the%20company%20has%20the%20reach%2C%20name%20recognition%2C%20and%20market%20cap%20to%20square%20up%20against%20any%20of%20the%20industry's%20giants.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20take%20out%20the%20king%2C%26quot%3B%20Jack%20Miller%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20T3%20Sixty%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20management%20consulting%20firm%2C%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20the%20challenge%20of%20the%20week%20is%20for%20Zillow%2C%20I%20still%20think%20they're%20such%20a%20powerful%20player.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20question%2C%20though%2C%20that%20things%20are%20changing.%20Portals%20like%20Zillow%2C%20Redfin%2C%20and%20Realtor.com%20have%20never%20been%20able%20to%20show%20you%20%3Cem%3Eevery%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehome%20on%20the%20market%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20the%20internet%20age%2C%20agents%20have%20always%20quietly%20passed%20around%20some%20listings%20before%20launching%20them%20widely.%20But%20no%20company%20has%20leaned%20into%20this%20strategy%20like%20Compass.%20The%20firm's%20website%20is%20home%20to%20thousands%20of%20listings%20that%20don't%20appear%20on%20other%20sites%2C%20and%20its%20pending%20purchase%20of%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20real%20estate%20companies%20could%20dramatically%20expand%20that%20stockpile%20of%20%26quot%3Bexclusive%20inventory.%26quot%3B%20Meanwhile%2C%20other%20brokerage%20firms%20are%20erecting%20their%20own%20walled%20gardens%20or%20threatening%20to%20follow%20suit.%20Those%20in%20Zillow's%20camp%20warn%20that%20we're%20headed%20toward%20a%20world%20in%20which%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20large%20brokerages%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-listings-zillow-america-europe-france-italy-house-hunting-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtrol%20access%20to%20real%20estate%3C%2Fa%3E%20listings%2C%20muscling%20out%20smaller%20players%20and%20making%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-fight-clear-cooperation-realtors-zillow-pocket-listings-homes-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etougher%20for%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20their%20dream%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20scenario%20is%20still%20a%20long%20way%20off%2C%20says%20Mike%20DelPrete%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20tech%20strategist%20and%20scholar-in-residence%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%20Boulder.%20But%20Compass's%20latest%20blockbuster%20deal%20marks%20yet%20another%20move%20in%20that%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%2010%20years%20from%20now%20we're%20looking%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20DelPrete%20tells%20me%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20could%20easily%20imagine%20looking%20at%20this%20moment%20and%20saying%2C%20'Yes%2C%20that's%20when%20it%20all%20changed.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20serious%20of%20Zillow's%20legal%20threats%20is%20also%20the%20most%20recent.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20sued%20the%20search%20giant%20and%20one%20of%20its%20rivals%2C%20Redfin%2C%20over%20a%20%24100%20million%20deal%20the%20pair%20made%20in%20February.%20Under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20the%20two%20companies%20would%20share%20advertisements%20for%20multifamily%20rental%20properties%20(think%3A%20apartments%20and%20condos)%20across%20their%20respective%20sites%20and%20subsidiaries%2C%20including%20Rent.com%20and%20ApartmentGuide.com.%20The%20FTC's%20antitrust%20complaint%20accuses%20the%20companies%20of%20turning%20Redfin's%20sites%20into%20%26quot%3Ba%20copy%20of%20the%20listings%20that%20appear%20on%20Zillow's%20sites%2C%26quot%3B%20destroying%20competition%20while%20driving%20up%20costs%20for%20property%20managers%20and%20apartment%20hunters.%20A%20Zillow%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement%20that%20the%20arrangement%20actually%20benefits%20those%20groups%20and%20has%20%26quot%3Bexpanded%20renters'%20access%20to%20multifamily%20listings%20across%20multiple%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20helping%20property%20managers%20fill%20vacancies%20and%20renters%20find%20homes.%20A%20Redfin%20spokesperson%20made%20a%20similar%20argument%2C%20writing%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bstrongly%20disagrees%20with%20the%20FTC's%20allegations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20far%20from%20the%20only%20major%20lawsuit%20looming%20over%20Zillow.%20In%20late%20July%2C%20the%20real%20estate%20firm%20CoStar%20sued%20Zillow%20for%20copyright%20infringement%20and%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20in%20damages%2C%20claiming%20the%20search%20giant%20had%20cribbed%20some%2046%2C000%20CoStar-watermarked%20photos%20for%20use%20on%20its%20own%20website.%20Then%2C%20on%20Sept.%2022%2C%20a%20pair%20of%20big-time%20plaintiffs'%20law%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20firms%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agents-lawsuits-buy-sell-homes-forever-housing-market-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantitrust%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20real%20estate%20industry%20resulted%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-housing-market-homebuying-agents-commissions-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24418%20million%20settlement%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rewrote%20the%20rules%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuyers-sellers-realtor-agent-commissions-saving-rule-changes-lawsuit-settlement-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagent%20commissions%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20filed%20a%20class-action%20suit%20against%20Zillow.%20They%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20effectively%20driving%20up%20real%20estate%20costs%20by%20directing%20buyers%20to%20work%20with%20agents%20who%20pay%20Zillow%20as%20much%20as%2040%25%20of%20their%20commission%20from%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20too%20early%20to%20say%20what%20will%20become%20of%20the%20FTC%20lawsuit.%20As%20for%20the%20other%20two%20complaints%2C%20there's%20a%20chance%20they%20cost%20Zillow%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20really%20surprising.%20CoStar%2C%20which%20owns%20rival%20home-search%20website%20Homes.com%2C%20maintains%20a%20long-running%20feud%20with%20Zillow.%20The%20company%20has%20spent%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20on%20technology%20and%20splashy%20ads%20to%20boost%20its%20search%20offering%2C%20but%20has%20so%20far%20failed%20to%20make%20a%20real%20dent%20in%20Zillow's%20market%20share.%20CoStar's%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostar-ceo-andrew-florance-employee-treatment-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndy%20Florance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20publicly%20backed%20Compass%20in%20the%20fight%20over%20real%20estate%20listings%20and%2C%20in%20April%2C%20memorably%20bashed%20Zillow%20in%20a%20mass%20email%20to%20real%20estate%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20class-action%20suit%2C%20the%20plaintiffs'%20firms%20may%20have%20sensed%20an%20opportunity%20to%20strike%20at%20Zillow%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20weakness.%20Or%20maybe%20they%20simply%20spied%20more%20meat%20on%20the%20bone%20after%20scoring%20a%20victory%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawsuits-verdict-realtors-brokerages-real-estate-agents-home-buying-selling-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20industry's%20largest%20brokerages.%20Zillow%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20has%20vowed%20to%20fight%20these%20claims.%20In%20an%20emailed%20statement%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20complaint%20%26quot%3Bfundamentally%20misrepresents%20how%20Zillow%20operates%20and%20the%20value%20we've%20delivered%20to%20buyers%2C%20sellers%2C%20and%20real%20estate%20professionals%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%26quot%3B%20The%20reaction%20around%20the%20industry%20has%20been%20mostly%20a%20shoulder%20shrug.%20One%20contracts%20law%20professor%2C%20writing%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20said%20the%20suit%20is%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20nowhere%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20over%20real%20estate%20listings%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20feels%20far%20more%20existential%20for%20Zillow.%20That's%20why%20the%20news%20last%20week%20that%20Compass%20had%20struck%20a%20%241.6%20billion%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edeal%20to%20acquire%20Anywhere%20Real%20Estate%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20real%20estate%20companies%20in%20the%20world%20and%20the%20owner%20of%20household%20names%20like%20Century21%2C%20Corcoran%2C%20and%20Coldwell%20Banker%20%E2%80%94%20overshadowed%20the%20legal%20threats.%20The%20combined%20entity%2C%20including%20franchisees%20and%20company-owned%20offices%2C%20would%20boast%20around%20216%2C000%20agents%20in%20the%20US%20and%20account%20for%20about%2024%25%20of%20the%20national%20sales%20volume%20based%20on%202024%20figures%2C%20data%20from%20T3%20Sixty%20shows.%20That%20kind%20of%20national%20market%20share%20is%20unheard%20of%20in%20a%20traditionally%20fragmented%20industry%2C%20and%20would%20almost%20surely%20give%20Compass%20more%20leverage%20in%20its%20showdown%20with%20Zillow.%20The%20advantage%20would%20be%20especially%20pronounced%20in%20cities%20like%20San%20Francisco%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20where%20the%20Compass%20and%20Anywhere%20brands%20easily%20combine%20for%20between%2030%25%20and%2050%25%20of%20the%20market%2C%20per%20data%20from%20T3%20Sixty.%20Any%20player%20of%20that%20size%20in%20a%20local%20market%20%26quot%3Bcan%20absolutely%20change%20the%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20core%2C%20this%20battle%20is%20about%20access%20to%20for-sale%20homes%3A%20who%20gets%20to%20see%20them%2C%20and%20where%20they%20have%20to%20go%20to%20find%20them.%20Compass's%20Reffkin%20has%20spent%20the%20past%20year%20promoting%20a%20%26quot%3Bthree-phased%20marketing%20strategy%26quot%3B%20that%20encourages%20agents%20and%20their%20clients%20to%20market%20homes%20exclusively%20on%20the%20brokerage's%20website%20before%20sharing%20them%20with%20the%20industry%20databases%20known%20as%20multiple%20listing%20services.%20Those%20databases%20then%20funnel%20that%20information%20to%20agents%2C%20brokerages%2C%20and%20search%20portals%20such%20as%20Zillow.%20Most%20agents%20share%20homes%20on%20the%20MLS%20pretty%20much%20as%20soon%20as%20they're%20for%20sale.%20Compass%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20offers%20buyers%20who%20visit%20its%20website%20or%20work%20with%20one%20of%20its%20agents%20an%20inside%20track%20on%20some%20of%20its%20most%20desirable%20properties.%20The%20strategy%2C%20Reffkin%20argues%2C%20also%20gives%20sellers%20the%20chance%20to%20test%20the%20waters%20and%20tinker%20with%20pricing%20before%20sharing%20their%20listing%20on%20sites%20like%20Zillow%2C%20which%20tracks%20price%20cuts%20and%20the%20number%20of%20days%20a%20house%20has%20been%20on%20the%20market%20%E2%80%94%20information%20he%20claims%20puts%20sellers%20at%20a%20disadvantage%20in%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZillow%20has%20a%20clear%20interest%20in%20stamping%20out%20the%20three-phased%20model%3A%20Its%20search%20portal%20suddenly%20looks%20a%20lot%20less%20valuable%20to%20buyers%20if%20big%20brokerages%20like%20Compass%20are%20hoarding%20listings%20on%20their%20own%20websites.%20Zillow%20also%20claims%20that%20Compass's%20strategy%20is%20bad%20for%20consumers%2C%20period.%20In%20June%2C%20Zillow%20tried%20to%20strike%20back%20at%20Compass%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-ban-blacklist-real-estate-listings-what-homebuyers-can-do-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanning%20listings%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20its%20site%20that%20had%20been%20advertised%20publicly%20for%20more%20than%20one%20business%20day%20%E2%80%94%20via%20a%20post%20on%20a%20brokerage's%20website%2C%20say%2C%20or%20a%20sign%20in%20a%20front%20yard%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ewithout%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20shared%20widely%20in%20the%20MLS.%20Some%20executives%20I%20spoke%20to%20around%20this%20time%20likened%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BZillow%20Ban%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20checkmate%20move%2C%20forcing%20agents%20to%20explain%20to%20their%20sellers%20why%20their%20homes%20would%20never%20appear%20on%20Zillow.%20Compass%20responded%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-real-estate-listings-compass-lawsuit-agents-home-search-buying-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuing%20Zillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20federal%20court%2C%20claiming%20the%20company%20was%20using%20its%20monopolistic%20power%20to%20quash%20an%20innovative%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20thing%3A%20Zillow's%20supposed%20crackdown%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20have%20done%20much%20of%20anything.%20Reffkin%20and%20Co.%20are%20still%20going%20full%20steam%20ahead%20on%20their%20three-phased%20strategy.%20A%20recent%20analysis%20of%20Compass%20data%20by%20DelPrete%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%20researcher%2C%20found%20that%20the%20company's%20volume%20of%20%26quot%3Bexclusive%20inventory%26quot%3B%20has%20held%20firm%20despite%20Zillow's%20new%20policy%20%E2%80%94%20Compass%20maintains%20a%20trove%20of%20more%20than%208%2C000%20listings%20that%20can't%20be%20found%20anywhere%20else%2C%20roughly%20in%20line%20with%20May%20levels.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20company%20is%20poised%20to%20expand%20its%20walled%20garden%20with%20the%20Anywhere%20acquisition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20chess%20game%20of%20lawsuits%20and%20buyouts%2C%20each%20side%20has%20plenty%20of%20moves%20left%20to%20make.%20It'll%20likely%20be%20at%20least%20a%20year%20before%20the%20Anywhere%20deal%20clears%20regulatory%20hurdles%20and%20the%20ink%20dries.%20Even%20then%2C%20Reffkin%20will%20face%20the%20daunting%20task%20of%20spreading%20the%20Compass%20gospel%20to%20thousands%20of%20franchisees%20and%20agents%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agents-realtors-reckoning-housing-market-home-sales-slow-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20as%20independent%20contractors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20are%20free%20to%20move%20to%20another%20brokerage%20if%20they%20clash%20with%20the%20exclusive-inventory%20strategy%20or%20any%20other%20facets%20of%20Compass's%20business.%20DelPrete%20has%20for%20years%20warned%20that%20the%20real%20estate%20industry%20could%20devolve%20into%20its%20own%20version%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstreaming-tv-movies-music-expensive-unequal-spotify-netflix-taylor-swift-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentertainment%20streaming%20wars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20behemoths%20racing%20to%20gobble%20up%20content%20for%20their%20own%20platforms.%20Stacking%20up%20exclusive%20%26quot%3Bcontent%26quot%3B%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20however%2C%20isn't%20as%20easy%20as%20it%20is%20in%20Hollywood.%20Disney%20can%20buy%20up%20Marvel%2C%20flip%20a%20switch%2C%20and%20make%20all%20those%20superhero%20movies%20available%20exclusively%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-plus-price-increase-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDisney%2B%20subscribers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20can%20force%20a%20home%20seller%20to%20list%20their%20home%20as%20a%20p