ng%20this%20product%20line.%20We're%20going%20to%20move%202%2C000%20engineers%20off%20of%20project%20X%20onto%20project%20Y%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Haas%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20company%20had%20only%20about%206%2C000%20people%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20abrupt%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20away%20from%20making%20support%20chips%20for%20Intel's%20processors%20%E2%80%94%20proved%20decisive.%20Instead%20of%20trying%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20Intel%20in%20PCs%2C%20Huang%20redirected%20thousands%20of%20engineers%20to%20focus%20on%20Arm-based%20designs%20and%20graphics%20chips.%20That%20move%20reshaped%20the%20company's%20future%2C%20said%20Haas%2C%20who%20left%20Nvidia%20in%202013%20to%20join%20Arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20this%20amazing%20set%20of%20characteristics%20of%20vision%2C%20speed%2C%20fearlessness%2C%20taking%20risk%2C%20and%20an%20ability%20to%20pivot%20very%2C%20very%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20Haas%20said%20of%20Huang%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Blearned%20so%20much%26quot%3B%20from%20working%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20one%20of%20Arm's%20flagship%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20its%20latest%20AI%20chips%20combine%20Arm-based%20CPUs%20with%20its%20own%20powerful%20GPUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Nvidia%20tried%20to%20acquire%20Arm%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farms-president-nvidia-merger-same-business-model-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2440%20billion%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20fell%20through%20because%20of%20regulatory%20hurdles.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farm-ceo-rene-haas-softbank-40-billion-nvidia-deal-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHaas%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20that%20Arm%20wasn't%20dwelling%20on%20the%20failed%20sale%20and%20was%20instead%20focused%20on%20expanding%20in%20industries%20like%20cloud%2C%20networking%2C%20automotive%2C%20and%20the%20Internet%20of%20Things.%3C%2Fp%3E