EIf%20the%20shutdown%20persists%20into%20mid-October%2C%20it%20could%20impact%20the%20publication%20of%20inflation%20indicators.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20month's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faugust-jobs-report-unemployment-rate-employment-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejobs%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20coming%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-is-government-shutting-down-explainer-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egovernment%20has%20shut%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Congress%20failed%20to%20pass%20a%20spending%20bill%20before%20the%2012%3A01%20a.m.%20Wednesday%20deadline.%20Depending%20on%20how%20long%20it%20goes%20on%2C%20that%20could%20affect%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics'%20reports%20that%20help%20businesses%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20know%20what's%20happening%20in%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20Department%20of%20Labor's%20contingency%20plan%2C%20if%20the%20government%20shutdown%20is%20still%20happening%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20monthly%20employment%20situation%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20the%20jobs%20report%2C%20won't%20be%20published%20as%20planned.%20If%20it's%20still%20happening%20by%20mid-October%2C%20it%20could%20affect%20the%20annual%20cost-of-living%20adjustment%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-social-security%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESocial%20Security%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20inflation%20data%20wouldn't%20be%20released%20on%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Labor%20said%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20would%20%26quot%3Bsuspend%20all%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20planned%20publications%20wouldn't%20be%20released%2C%20data%20collection%20would%20stop%2C%20and%20its%20website%20wouldn't%20be%20updated%20during%20the%20funding%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elapse.%20If%20it%20continues%20for%20a%20while%2C%20planned%20data%20releases%20could%20be%20delayed%2C%20and%20could%20affect%20data%20quality%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202013%20government%20shutdown%2C%20the%20September%20jobs%20report%20was%20delayed%20about%20two%20weeks%2C%20and%20the%20subsequent%20October%20report%20was%20delayed%20a%20week%20%26quot%3Bto%20allow%20enough%20time%20to%20collect%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20shutdown%2C%20BLS%20said.%20In%20the%20longest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-timeline-deadline-trump-democrats-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20government%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20took%20place%20in%20late%202018%20and%20early%202019%20during%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20the%20BLS%20was%20funded%2C%20so%20data%20collection%20wasn't%20affected%2C%20and%20reports%20were%20released%20as%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jobs%20report%20helps%20job%20seekers%20have%20a%20better%20understanding%20about%20labor%20demand%2C%20how%20many%20people%20are%20competing%20for%20job%20offers%2C%20and%20what%20earnings%20look%20like.%20Job%20growth%20in%20the%20past%20two%20reports%20was%20below%20expectations%2C%20and%20although%20unemployment%20is%20low%2C%20it%20has%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jobs%20report%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20monthly%20reports%20that%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20publishes.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-august-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsumer%20price%20index%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20producer%20price%20index%20are%20key%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einflation%20indicators%2C%20and%20the%20shutdown%20could%20delay%20their%20release.%20Labor%20market%20and%20inflation%20data%20help%20the%20Fed%20make%20decisions%20for%20its%20dual%20mandate%20balancing%20maximum%20employment%20and%20stable%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consumer%20price%20index%20and%20producer%20price%20index%20are%20scheduled%20to%20run%20on%20October%2015%20and%20October%2016%2C%20respectively.%20Real%20earnings%2C%20which%20the%20BLS%20uses%20the%20consumer%20price%20index%20to%20calculate%20and%20average%20hourly%20earnings%20from%20the%20jobs%20report%2C%20are%20also%20supposed%20to%20be%20published%20on%20October%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20the%20Social%20Security%20Administration%20evaluates%20whether%20to%20increase%20Social%20Security%20benefits%20with%20a%20cost-of-living%20adjustment%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fconsumer-price-index%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsumer%20price%20index%20inflation%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%20the%20year.%20Without%20September's%20result%20rounding%20out%20that%20third-quarter%20data%2C%20it%20could%20delay%20the%20announcement%20that%20typically%20comes%20out%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJos%C3%A9%20Torres%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20Interactive%20Brokers%2C%20said%20in%20written%20commentary%20that%20%26quot%3Ban%20extended%20halt%26quot%3B%20would%20affect%20both%20consumer%20spending%20and%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20immediate%20economic%20impact%20would%20be%20tangible%2C%26quot%3B%20Gregory%20Daco%2C%20EY's%20chief%20economist%2C%20said%20in%20a%20newsletter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20week%20of%20shutdown%20could%20reduce%20Q4%20GDP%20by%200.1%20percentage%20points%20(annualized)%2C%20or%20about%20%247%20billion%20per%20week%20%E2%80%94%20largely%20due%20to%20lost%20wages%2C%20procurement%20delays%20and%20softer%20final%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Daco%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fiscal%20drag%20would%20eventually%20be%20partially%20offset%20by%20back%20pay%20and%20a%20rebound%20in%20activity%2C%20but%20the%20confidence%20hit%20to%20markets%20and%20consumers%20could%20prove%20longer%20lasting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-jobs-report-bls-economic-data-job-seekers-fed-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759291265000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dc11d71c1f80efbec49b63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-jobs-report-bls-economic-data-job-seekers-fed-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20shutdown%20means%20there%20could%20be%20no%20jobs%20report%20this%20Friday%20unless%20things%20are%20resolved%20before%20then.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Madison%20Hoff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-jobs-report-bls-economic-data-job-seekers-fed-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20shut%20down.%20Federal%20workers%20are%20gearing%20up%20for%20mass%20firings.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Capitol%20building%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dbdb331c1f80efbec491fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump's%20administration%20warned%20that%20a%20government%20shutdown%20could%20lead%20to%20federal%20worker%20firings.%3Cp%3EBonnie%20Cash%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20has%20shut%20down%2C%20beginning%20at%2012%3A01%20a.m.%20on%20October%201.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20OMB%20told%20federal%20agencies%20to%20consider%20firing%20workers%20permanently.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20would%20be%20a%20step%20beyond%20the%20temporary%20furloughs%20that%20usually%20accompany%20a%20shutdown.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20has%20shut%20down%2C%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efederal%20workers'%20jobs%20are%20once%20again%20on%20the%20chopping%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublican%20and%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20failed%20to%20reach%20an%20agreement%20on%20a%20plan%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-is-government-shutting-down-explainer-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekeep%20the%20government%20funded%3C%2Fa%3E%20past%20September%2030.%20While%20the%20GOP%20controls%20Congress%20and%20the%20White%20House%2C%20passing%20a%20funding%20bill%20requires%2060%20Senate%20votes%20under%20current%20rules%2C%20meaning%20some%20Democrats%20need%20to%20be%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20workers'%20jobs%20are%20on%20the%20line%20%E2%80%94%20they%20could%20be%20fired%2C%20not%20just%20furloughed%2C%20as%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20prior%20government%20shutdowns.%20The%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20wrote%20a%20memo%20to%20federal%20agencies%20last%20week%20directing%20them%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-mass-firing-federal-workers-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bconsider%26quot%3B%20terminations%20for%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20working%20in%20programs%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20consistent%20with%20the%20President's%20priorities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20waited%20for%20the%20news%2C%20over%20a%20dozen%20federal%20workers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Tuesday%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20shutdown%20that%20they%20were%20meeting%20the%20uncertainty%20with%20feelings%20of%20anger%2C%20fear%2C%20and%20indifference.%20In%20the%20hours%20before%20the%20shutdown%2C%20some%20agencies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-federal-workers-read-email-furlough-warning-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esent%20emails%20to%20their%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20blaming%20Democrats%20for%20blocking%20a%20funding%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Department%20of%20Defense%20worker%20said%20their%20office%20won't%20be%20affected%20by%20furloughs%2C%20so%20they're%20not%20too%20worried.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20Department%20of%20the%20Interior%20employee%20said%20that%20the%20threat%20of%20terminations%20is%20weighing%20on%20workers%2C%20and%20another%20federal%20employee%20said%20that%20while%20they've%20dealt%20with%20the%20threat%20of%20imminent%20shutdowns%20before%2C%20just%20to%20have%20them%20averted%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20this%20time%20feels%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20you%20a%20federal%20worker%3F%20How%20is%20the%20government%20shutdown%20affecting%20you%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20via%20Signal%20at%20asheffey.97%20or%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20non-work%20device%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OMB%20memo%20did%20not%20indicate%20how%20many%20workers%20it%20is%20targeting%20through%20the%20reduction-in-force%20directive.%20When%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnancycordes%2Fstatus%2F1973008849255666022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easked%20by%20reporters%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20firings%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20%26quot%3Bmay%20do%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%20The%20White%20House%20and%20OMB%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20lawmakers%20intended%20to%20use%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20shutdown%20as%20a%20negotiating%20tool%20to%20receive%20policy%20wins%2C%20mostly%20around%