to%20be%20disrupted.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ed.gov%2Fmedia%2Fdocument%2Fus-department-of-education-contingency-plan-lapse-fiscal-year-fy-2026-appropriations-112431.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtingency%20plan%20said%20%3C%2Fa%3Eit%20plans%20to%20furlough%201%2C485%20of%20its%201%2C700%20employees.%20It%20will%20cease%20new%20grantmaking%20activities%20and%20pause%20reviews%20of%20civil%20rights%20complaints%20while%20continuing%20to%20disburse%20student%20loans%20and%20Pell%20Grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Labor%20is%20also%20planning%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dol.gov%2Fsites%2Fdolgov%2Ffiles%2Fgeneral%2Fplans%2Fdol-contingency-plan.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecease%20some%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20shutdown%2C%20including%20data%20collection%20through%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics.%20It%20means%20that%2C%20should%20the%20shutdown%20continue%20through%20Friday%2C%20the%20jobs%20report%20would%20not%20be%20released.%20The%20Social%20Security%20Administration's%20plan%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Fagency%2Fshutdown%2Fmaterials%2Fcontingency-plan-09-24-25.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epayments%20will%20continue%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20disbursed%20to%20recipients%2C%20but%20tasks%20like%20overpayment%20processing%20and%20benefit%20verifications%20will%20cease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OMB%20notice%20said%20that%20reduction-in-force%20notices%20are%20in%20addition%20to%20any%20furlough%20notices%20agencies%20send%20out%20during%20the%20shutdown%2C%20meaning%20that%20impacted%20employees%20are%20expected%20to%20receive%20two%20separate%20notices%20if%20they%20are%20both%20furloughed%20and%20included%20in%20termination%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20has%20already%20fired%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnumber-workers-