ure%20a%20%26quot%3BB%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20launch%20a%20government-run%20website%2C%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumprx-website-announcement-white-house-pfizer-ceo-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrumpRx.gov%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20consumers%20to%20buy%20prescription%20drugs%20directly%20from%20manufacturers%20on%20the%20site%20without%20the%20involvement%20of%20Pharmacy%20Benefit%20Managers%20as%20intermediaries.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Fsections%2Fshots-health-news%2F2025%2F09%2F30%2Fnx-s1-5558432%2Fdrug-prices-trumprx-pfizer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20NPR%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20administration%20expects%20to%20release%20the%20website%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%2C%20the%20billionaire%20venture%20capitalist%2C%20commented%20on%20X%20that%20this%20would%20be%20good%20for%20patients%20and%20could%20actually%20boost%20business%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-why-he-started-cost-plus-drugs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECost%20Plus%20Drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20runs%20on%20a%20similar%20model.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20has%20%26quot%3Bsome%20great%20people%20working%20on%20this%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bgive%20the%20program%2C%20and%20what%20we%20know%2C%20as%20of%20today%2C%20a%20grade%20of%20B.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20not%20an%20A%3F%20The%20stock%20prices%20of%20PBMs%20didn't%20get%20crushed%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Cuban.%20%26quot%3BWhich%20means%2C%20so%20far%2C%20no%20one%20expects%20much%20change%20for%20them.%20Which%20they%20expect%20they%20will%20make%20up%20lost%20revenues%20from%20patients%2C%20companies%2C%20and%20other%20payers%20elsewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20rigged%20to%20benefit%20the%20big%20PBMs%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20added%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20asking%20if%20Trump's%20operation%20could%20run%20honestly%20without%20favor.%20%26quot%3BThat%20said%2C%20it%20has%20a%20chance%20if%20they%20force%20PBMs%20to%20change.%20If%20that%20happens%2C%20Trump%20gets%20all%20the%20credit%20and%20it%20will%20be%20deserved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Cuban%20said%20of%20TrumpRx.gov%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20just%20a%20listing%20site..%20And%20as%20long%20as%20they%20include%20Cost%20Plus%20Drugs%2C%20given%20we%20typically%20have%20the%20lowest%20prices%20for%20more%20than%2090%25%20of%20prescriptions%2C%20I'm%20all%20for%20it!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20announcement%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpfizer-ceo-trump-tariffs-stopping-tremendous-investments-in-us-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPfizer%3C%2Fa%3E%20plans%20to%20offer%20some%20of%20its%20drugs%20on%20TrumpRx.gov%20and%20all%20of%20its%20drugs%20for%20Medicaid%20at%20a%20reduced%20rate.%20The%20deal%20grants%20the%20pharmaceutical%20manufacturer%20a%20three-year%20exemption%20from%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20The%20large%20majority%20of%20the%20Company's%20primary%20care%20treatments%20and%20some%20select%20specialty%20brands%20will%20be%20offered%20at%20savings%20that%20will%20range%20as%20high%20as%2085%25%20and%20on%20average%2050%25%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban's%20online%20pharmacy%2C%20which%20he%20founded%20alongside%20radiologist%20Alex%20Oshmyansky%20in%202022%2C%20Cost%20Plus%20Drugs%2C%20also%20eliminates%20intermediaries%20and%20offers%20drugs%20at%20a%2015%25%20markup%20above%20the%20manufacturer's%20wholesale%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Data%20from%20the%20Commonwealth%20Fund%2C%20around%2080%25%20of%20access%20to%20drugs%20in%20the%20US%20is%20controlled%20by%20three%20large%20PBMs%2C%20namely%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funitedhealth-q1-earnings-cut-outlook-medicare-alignment-stock-selloff-insurance-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUnitedHealth%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E-owned%20Optum%20Rx%2C%20CVS%20Health's%20Caremark%2C%20and%20Cigna's%20Express%20Scripts.%20Stock%20prices%20for%20all%20three%20parent%20companies%20did%20not%20substantially%20change%20throughout%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPBMs%20receive%20rebates%20from%20drug%20manufacturers%20in%20exchange%20for%20giving%20drugs%20favorable%20placement%20on%20formularies.%20Rebates%20are%20often%20tied%20to%20the%20list%20price%2C%20therefore%2C%20higher-priced%20drugs%20can%20generate%20larger%20rebates.%20That%20creates%20an%20incentive%20for%20PBMs%20to%20favor%20certain%20brand-name%20drugs%20over%20cheaper%20generics%20or%20biosimilars%20if%20the%20manufacturer%20offers%20a%20bigger%20rebate.%20Insurers%20say%20these%20rebates%20help%20lower%20overall%20costs.%20Critics%20argue%20the%20system%20inflates%20prices%20and%20contributes%20to%20higher%20insurance%20premiums%20for%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-responds-to-trumprx-venture-make-drugs-more-affordable-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759287762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6846f646f748d8c055f34b1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-responds-to-trumprx-venture-make-drugs-more-affordable-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20billionaire%20owner%20of%20Cost%20Plus%20Drugs%20is%20giving%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20announced%20website%2C%20TrumpRx.gov%2C%20a%20%26quot%3BB%26quot%3B%20for%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Ka